job_duty:
我们在寻找一位富有创造力、热衷于将数字项目变为现实，有热忱的网站开发人员加入我们的团队。来全面支持腾讯官网栏目的开发和日常维护，支持CRM系统的实施和持续运营。希望你熟悉公司IT基础架构和安全协议，能利用技术解决方案来不断吸引我们的内容受众。

你需要：
负责腾讯官网栏目的建设维护，包括但不限于流程自动化、自动化测试、代码质量管理、开发测试环境及新技术预研的前端/全栈开发工作;
协助项目管理，优化提升网站体验，完善CRM系统实施，提升其他与数字相关系统项目的运营;
衔接、解决国际传讯小组与腾讯内部，以及外部供应商在技术上的问题，保证沟通顺畅性与期望值一致；
协助管理社交网络后端；
能持续不断寻找新技术来提升国际传讯组的全球化交流。

We are seeking a creative web developer with a passion for bringing digital projects to life to join our team. The right candidate will help oversee website development and daily maintenance, the implementation and ongoing operation of a CRM, be intimately familiar with corporate IT infrastructure and security protocols, and bring new ideas that leverage technology solutions to enhance how we interact with our audiences. 

Oversee the daily operation of the company website including uploading new material, troubleshooting, and maintaining a thorough understanding of corporate IT infrastructure;
Assist in project management, particularly a pipeline of improvements to the website experience, implementation of a CRM, and other digital-related projects;
Serve as a key conduit between Global Communications, internal stakeholders, and external vendors on technical issues, ensure good communications and alignment of expectations;
Assist on managing the backend of social networks;
Stay current on web technologies and look for opportunities to leverage technology to support Global Communications;

